  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p>*Supervise and coordinate the daily operations of the foods service and preparation, quality standards, and ensuring compliance with health and safety regulations.</p><p>*Provide guidance, training, and support to maximize team performance.</p><p>*Ensure that all food areas are cleaned and sanitized according to food safety standards.</p><p>*Ensure that all policies and procedures are followed by the staff.</p><p>*Resolve customer complaints and concerns regarding food service.</p><p>*Able to lift and carry heavy items, roughly 20KG.</p><p>*Need working on Saturday, Sunday, Public Holiday and overtime.</p><p>*Able to work rotate shift and overtime.</p><p>Working Location: Stall Location<br /><br /><u><strong>Requirements:</strong></u></p><ul><li>At least 2 Year(s) of working experience and have experience in the related field is required for this position.</li><li>Must possess at least higher Education/Diploma in any field.</li><li>Strong leadership skills and management competencies.</li><li>Excellent communication skills with teams and customers.</li><li>Strategic & critical thinking as well as decision-making and negotiation skills.</li><li>Able to adapt, prioritize, manage pressure, multitask and work independently.</li><li>Time management/ meticulous and mature in work.</li></ul>",
